== Itabi ry'umwotsi ==[[File:Nicotiana.jpg|thumb|Nicotiana]]
Itabi ni kimwe mu biyobyabwenge banywa cyangwa se basohora umwotsi.

[[Itabi]] rikorwa hifashishishijwe ibibabi ,abahanga mu by'ubuzima bavugako

kurubu hariho ubwoko burenga 70 bw'itabi<ref>https://umutihealth.com/kunywa-itabi/</ref> . mu [[Rwanda]] nahandi kw'Isi.

== Ingaruka z'iterwa n'itabi ==
kunywa itabi byangiza mu buryo bukomeye bitewe nuko umwotsi w'itabi 

habamo ikinyabutabire kitwa [[Itabi|nikotine]],ifite ubushobozi bwo kwangiza 

uturemangingo twubatse [[ubwonko]], ndetse bukangiza ubushobozi bwo gufata 

Abahanga bavugako [[Itabi|nikotine]] ihagarika ubudahangarwa bwo kurema 

uturemangingo dusimbura utwangiritse.<ref>https://agakiza.org/Waruziko-kunywa-itabi-byangiza-ingingo-zose-zubatse-umuntu.html</ref>

